                <li><strong>Feedback:</strong> We may provide feedback or request modifications to your User Content before approval.</li>
                <li><strong>Removal After Publication:</strong> We reserve the right to remove previously published User Content if it is found to violate this Agreement or if we receive valid complaints.</li>
            </ol>

            <h3>5. User Responsibilities:</h3>

            <ol>
                <li><strong>Email Verification:</strong> You agree to maintain a verified email address for communication regarding your submissions.</li>
                <li><strong>Response to Inquiries:</strong> You agree to respond to reasonable inquiries from SQLtest regarding your User Content.</li>
                <li><strong>Updates and Corrections:</strong> You may be asked to update or correct your User Content if errors or issues are identified.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Standards:</strong> You agree to uphold our community standards and contribute positively to the learning environment.</li>
